I"<h1 class="no_toc" id="minimize-memory-storage">Minimize Memory Storage</h1>

<h2 class="no_toc text-delta" id="table-of-contents">Table of contents</h2>
<hr />
<p>Memory space is expensive in most deployments.  It also directly impacts the performance of the solution.</p>

<p>A best practice is to minimize the amount of data stored in memory at any point.</p>

<ul>
  <li>Overwrite data and delete data whenever possible</li>
  <li>Avoid having a large amount of data in memory. Instead, use Database or files</li>
</ul>
